---
import MarketingLayout from "../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro";
---

<MarketingLayout title="Privacy Policy - BuffBook" description="Privacy Policy for BuffBook">
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tight text-foreground mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-muted-foreground">
      <p class="mb-4">Last updated: June 2026</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We collect information to provide better services to our users. This includes:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> When you create an account, we collect your email address and authentication credentials.</li>
        <li><strong>Fitness & Assessment Data:</strong> If you apply for a custom mesocycle plan, you voluntarily provide physical metrics, injury history, and training goals. This is sensitive information used strictly for creating your customized plan.</li>
        <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> We do not store credit card details. Payments are processed securely via our third-party payment processors.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> We use Google Analytics to understand how our site is used and to improve the user experience.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Information</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We use the information we collect to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
        <li>Provide, maintain, and improve BuffBook and our custom coaching services.</li>
        <li>Process transactions and send related information, including confirmations and receipts.</li>
        <li>Send you technical notices, updates, and support messages.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">3. Data Sharing and Security</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We do not sell your personal information. We may share information with trusted third-party service providers (like payment processors and analytics providers) strictly to operate our business.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">4. Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Depending on your location (e.g., GDPR in Europe, CCPA in California), you may have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information. If you wish to delete your account and all associated fitness data, please contact us.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</MarketingLayout>
